    </header>

    <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-12 pb-8">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-display-sm md:text-display mb-4">
        Suhas Darsi
      </h1>
      <p class="text-body text-muted-foreground mb-6 leading-relaxed">
        Co-Founder at <a href="https://superalign.ai" class="text-foreground underline decoration-2 decoration-[#a19c87] underline-offset-4">SuperAlign</a>, building foundational infrastructure for AI safety. We help security teams see, understand, and control AI adoption across their organizations.
      </p>
      <p class="text-body text-muted-foreground mb-6 leading-relaxed">
        My background is in Computer Vision research at IIIT Hyderabad. Today I spend most of my time thinking about AI governance, the security risks of enterprise AI, and what it takes to build trustworthy systems at scale.
      </p>
      <p class="text-body text-muted-foreground mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        <a href="/blog" class="text-foreground underline decoration-2 decoration-[#a19c87] underline-offset-4">Writing</a> about AI security, network theory, building products, and self-hosting — observations from trying to ship real things in a fast-moving space.
